snippet.textDisplay:
Amazing video! And I love both kinds of SUVs. Boxy or Curvy, SUV is an SUV. And talking about the Porche Cayenne, it's love at first sight 👻
PS. it doesn't make the Mercedes G class amg bad or anything. It's more like a healthy competition.

Just like the new Safari and the new Scorpio N. I own the Safari and I'd love to add that both our desi SUVs are capable offroaders, have great city presence and are very good cars. Though the Scorpio clearly beats the Safari in offroading, but still our Desi SUVs are giving superb competition to everyone in India. Isn't it?
